# install the following python packages: 

```
NumPy - a math library. We use NumPy arrays (nparray) quite a lot.
SciPy - A collection of functions for scientific computing. Also scipy.sparse provides sparse matrices.
pandas -   
matplotlib
jupyter-notebook
iPython
scikit-learn
```

# on mac, you can do: 

```
brew cask install anaconda
```

This installs the anaconda distribution, which has all the above tools plus python3. 

